Barista Bar Terms and Conditions
Updated Wednesday 9th October 2024
These are the terms and conditions applicable to the beverage/merchandise based rewards scheme tied to purchase behaviour ("Barista Bar Loyalty Scheme"), the My Barista Rewards+ mobile app from the Google Play or Apple stores ("Loyalty App") and website at www.mybaristabar.com (“Site”).
These terms and conditions govern the relationship between Henderson Foodservice Limited a company incorporated in Northern Ireland with company number NI006894 whose registered office is at 1 Hightown Ave, Newtownabbey, BT36 4RT ("Barista Bar", “our”, "we" or "us") and you; with these terms and conditions to be referred to hereafter as the “Terms and Conditions”.
The Barista Bar Loyalty Scheme, My Barista Bar Rewards+ mobile app, website (www.mybaristabar.com) and any sub-domains are operated by Barista Bar. Barista Bar offers this website, including all stories, information, tools and downloads ("Services") available from this site to you, the user, conditioned upon your acceptance of all terms, conditions, policies and notices stated here.
Please read these Terms and Conditions carefully before accessing or using our website, including all Services available from this site to you, the user. By visiting our website and/or registering for our Loyalty Scheme, you engage in our Services and agree to be bound by the following terms and conditions (“Terms and Conditions”, “Terms”), including those additional terms and conditions and policies referenced herein and/or available by hyperlink. These Terms and Conditions apply to all users of the site, including without limitation users who are browsers, vendors, customers, merchants, and/or contributors of content.
