Your usage of the Barista Bar Loyalty Scheme can be managed by downloading the Loyalty App or through an official, branded plastic card displaying your card number and barcode ("Card/Key Fob") . New Card/Key Fobs will be limited in circulation to pick up from store from 1st January 2024.
Any new features or tools which are added to the current website and Services shall also be subject to the Terms and Conditions. You can review the most current version of the Terms and Conditions at any time on this page. We reserve the right to update, change or replace any part of these Terms and Conditions by posting updates and/or changes to our website. It is your responsibility to check this page periodically for changes. You waive any right to receive specific notice of such changes. Your continued use of the website, including all Services available from this site to you, the user, will confirm your acceptance of such changes or modifications.
