We engage with three designated data processors to facilitate our Services to handle specific data processing activities, namely PDI Technologies (fulfilling Stamp loyalty redemptions at Point of Sale); Sugar Rush Creative Ltd (managing our Loyalty App and Reward+ merchandise Points) and dotdigital EMEA Limited (providing bespoke and automated email sends).
