Registering for the Scheme
Registering via our Loyalty App or using the details of a physical Card/Key Fob enables you to redeem the beverage related stamps ("Stamps") and merchandise related points ("Points") you have earned on certain purchases in participating Barista Bar outlets.
Stamps can be earned and redeemed instore using either the Loyalty App or a physical Card/Key Fob.
Rewards+ Points can only be earned if you are registered for the My Barista Bar Rewards+ Loyalty App; and can only be redeemed via the Loyalty App.
After 18th December 2023 you can join the Scheme by downloading the My Barista Bar Rewards+ Loyalty App from the Google Play or Apple App stores (which will be free of any charge) and following the registration process once installed on your device.
You must register to redeem your free coffee and other offers.
You can only register for the Scheme in the name of one individual with a single account per individual. You cannot register your account in the name of more than one individual or email address. You must use a legitimate, permanent email address to register.
You agree to provide current, complete and accurate account information for the individual registering. You agree to promptly update your account and other information, so that we can administer Services and contact you as needed.
This scheme is not targeted towards, nor intended for use by, anyone under the age of 16. Please read the Privacy Policy (
https://www.mybaristabar.com/privacy-policy
) carefully to understand how we use and disclose information about our customers.
Existing registered Barista Bar Loyalty Scheme users do not need to register a completely new account to use our My Barista Bar Rewards+ Loyalty App. Existing users can set up a mobile account using your existing Loyalty Card Number or the email address you provided when you originally registered. Any existing earned Stamps will then automatically appear on the homescreen of the Loyalty App, and you can then start to build up Points as well with each subsequent purchase. Your existing loyalty card/key fob will also continue to earn and redeem you Stamps if scanned at the till instore.
Use of the Scheme
You can use the Scheme at any participating Barista Bar outlet in Northern Ireland. This will include most SPAR, EUROSPAR, ViVO, ViVOXTRA or ViVO Essentials branded stores across Northern Ireland, with a limited number of exceptions.
You can use the Scheme, subject to the provisions of this Agreement, to earn Stamps and Points whenever you purchase a Barista Bar beverage eligible within the scheme. This only includes beverages served from the Barista Bar stand or in the Barista Bar café.
Barista Bar locations outside of Northern Ireland may operate their own loyalty offers but are not participants in this Scheme. Purchases from these stores will not earn Stamps or Reward+ Points within this Scheme, and these locations will not redeem Stamps for free coffees from purchases earned in Northern Ireland stores.
Stamps
Stamps can only be earned at the time of purchase and only if the Loyalty App or Card/Key Fob is presented at the time of payment. You will earn 1 Stamp for each Barista Bar beverage purchased. You can only collect Stamps for beverages served from the Barista Bar stand or in the Barista Bar café.
Once you have collected nine Stamps via the Loyalty App or your Card/Key Fob, you may use your Stamps to redeem one free hot beverage from a participating Barista Bar outlet. You may not make part payment for a purchase using Stamps. Stamps cannot be earned to the extent that a purchase is made with redeemed Stamps.
You can check your current Stamps balance on the Loyalty App, or on your receipt at the point of purchase at any participating Barista Bar outlet.
Rewards+ Points
Redeeming Rewards+ Points is exclusive to those who have downloaded and set up their Loyalty App. Points can only be earned at the time of purchase and only if the Loyalty App or Card/Key Fob is presented at the time of payment. You will earn 1 Point for each Barista Bar beverage purchased from the point you download and register to use the Loyalty App. You can only collect Points for beverages served from the Barista Bar stand or in the Barista Bar café.
You may use your Points to redeem free merchandise and special offers listed in the Rewards+ section of the Loyalty App. All redemptions must be managed through the Loyalty App. You may not use Points in any participating Barista Bar outlet as these cannot be exchanged for hot beverages or any other products instore. You may not make part payment for products using Points. Points cannot be earned to the extent that a purchase is made with redeemed Points.
You can check your current Points balance on the Loyalty App.
We reserve the right to alter the points value of any given offer without notice. The required value will automatically refresh beside each product within the Rewards+ section of the app.
Additionally, we reserve the right to add or remove offers such as merchandise or partner offers at our discretion without prior notice.
Please allow up to 28 days for the processing and delivery of any Rewards+ items that have been redeemed. If you haven't received your order after this period, you can email us at
hello@mybaristabar.com
.
Other benefits
On registration of your account, you will be gifted one free Barista Bar beverage to redeem in participating stores. Eligibility for this free coffee is limited to a single account per individual. If we have reasonable grounds to suspect abuse of the free registration beverage process, we reserve the right to suspend your account and take further action.
On sign up, you will be asked to specify your date of birth. Each year, you will be gifted one additional free Barista Bar beverage to redeem in participating stores. This free beverage will be added to your account to use from the Monday prior to your birthday that year, and will be available to redeem until the Sunday following your birthday that year. Any Birthday beverages not redeemed during your Birthday Week (Monday to Sunday) will then be removed from your account. Missed Birthday redemptions will not be reinstated and your date of birth will not be altered from what was provided during sign up.
General Usage
The Scheme cannot be used in conjunction with any discount or privilege card whether issued by us or by any third party.
Stamps and Points are personal to you. You cannot combine or pool Stamps or Points with those of another Scheme user and you cannot redeem Stamps or Points together with another Scheme user. You cannot transfer your Card/Key Fob or Loyalty App or any stored Stamps or Points on it to any other person.
Stamps and Points have no cash value. Stamps and Points can only be earned, retained and redeemed as set out in this Agreement. Any Stamps or Rewards+ Points obtained or used otherwise than in accordance with this Agreement will be invalid and cannot be redeemed. Once Stamps and Points are redeemed they become null and void and cannot be redeemed a second or more time.
Your Card/Key Fob or Loyalty App is not a credit card, charge card or debit card. Please note that your Card is issued by, and remains the property at all times of, Henderson Foodservice Limited.
Changes to your details
If you need to change any of the details you provided when you registered , you can update your details after registering for the Loyalty App at any time within the app, or by e-mailing
hello@mybaristabar.com
.
The email address associated with your account can only be changed by e-mailing
hello@mybaristabar.com
. We will ask you to confirm other account details to verify your identity before making any changes.
Loss, theft, damage
If your Card/Key Fob is lost, stolen or damaged you may lose any Stamps or Points you have earned.
If a device with your Loyalty App installed is lost, stolen or damaged you may lose any Stamps or Points you have earned.
Stamps and Points earned through using the Scheme are not covered by any compensation scheme.
You should immediately report any loss or theft of your Card/Key Fob or Loyalty App device, or any fraudulent or unauthorised use of your Loyalty account by emailing
hello@mybaristabar.com
.
If your Card/Key Fob or phone is lost, damaged or stolen or someone makes unauthorised use of your Account we may, at our sole and absolute discretion, transfer any Stamps or Points stored on your Card to a replacement account managed through the Loyalty App and/or re-credit any Stamps or Points redeemed without your consent.
If you subsequently find or retrieve a Card which you have reported lost or stolen, you must notify Customer Services immediately by emailing
hello@mybaristabar.com
.
Expiry and Cancellation
Your loyalty Account does not have an expiry date. However, Stamps are only valid so long as you have used your Card/Key Fob or the Loyalty App to earn Stamps in the previous 12 months. If your account has not been used in this way for 12 consecutive months, we reserve the right to remove Stamps, free registration beverages and birthday anniversary beverages from your account (as applicable).
Points must be used to redeem Rewards+ merchandise or offers within a 2 year period. We reserve the right to remove any Rewards+ points that have not been redeemed where the associated transaction date was more than 2 years ago.
Points that have expired or been removed as above cannot be transferred to a new account or reinstated. You have the right to cancel your account at any time by returning your loyalty card to Customer Services or uninstalling the Loyalty App from all devices. If you wish to cancel your involvement in the scheme altogether, please use the Delete Account function in the app or email
hello@mybaristabar.com
. If you cancel your account, you will lose the right to redeem all and any Stamps and Points that are unused at the time of cancellation.
We may, on notifying you, forfeit all accrued Stamps and Points, and/or suspend your right to collect and/or redeem Stamps and Points if you are in breach of this Agreement, if we have reasonable grounds to suspect that you are engaged in fraudulent or other criminal activities relating to us, your account, or if you supply false or misleading information to us.
Your Card/Key Fob and Loyalty App may only be used at participating Barista Bar outlets, which may be subject to change.
We reserve the right to terminate, discontinue, cancel or amend the Card/Key Fob or Loyalty App facility at any time without notice to you.
Complaints procedure
